                <h1>Why is My Google Background Black? Understand Dark Mode</h1>
                <p>The background on your Google turning black is likely due to the Dark Mode feature being enabled. This mode helps reduce eye strain in low light conditions and saves battery life on OLED screens. You can toggle this setting through your device or browser settings if you prefer the traditional white background.</p>
